Cube World is an action role-playing-game for the PC made by Wollay. It has been in development since June 2011.
With gameplay inspired by Diablo, Zelda, Minecraft, and many other classic Role-Playing Games, Cube World aims to be the perfect mix of RPG elements, exploration, action, and creation.
Infinite worlds, varying landscapes, missions, dungeons and castles. You can hike, boat and hang glide across the vast world that is generated.
Play as a Warrior, Ranger, Mage or Rogue as one of the 8 races. Tame a pet to help you with your adventures.
Get on a Multiplayer server and play with your friends.

Updates and patches:
* [NEW] - Added an option to limit the frame rate (see options menu: FPS limit; default 111 fps)
* [FIXED] - Ranger ability 'Scout's switftness' doesn't crash on multiplayer servers anymore
* [FIXED] Ranger ability 'Retreat' doesn't increase hang gliding speed anymore
* [FIXED] The crossbow's right mouse button ability now only does damage when charged
* [NEW] You can now reset the day in inns only between 6:00 P.M. and 6:00 A.M.
* [FIXED] Fixed a bug where multiplayer groups received too much XP for missions
